OL,3,CTeenagers to face trial after denying
OL,4,Cgirl's murder
OL,6,FThree teenagers have pleaded not
OL,7,Fguilty to murdering a 16-year old girl
OL,8,Fwho was stabbed to death in Leeds.
OL,10,FKayla Smith, 18, Archie Rycroft, 19,
OL,11,Fand a 17-year old boy, who cannot be
OL,12,Fnamed for legal reasons, appeared for
OL,13,Fa plea hearing at Leeds Crown Court on
OL,14,FFriday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
