OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1777662668
OL,3,CTeenagers to face trial after denying
OL,4,Cgirl's murder
OL,6,FAll three denied murdering Chloe
OL,7,FWatson Dransfield, who was found
OL,8,Funconscious at an address on
OL,9,FKennerleigh Avenue, in Austhorpe, in
OL,10,Fthe early hours of Saturday 28 March.
OL,11,FShe died in hospital a short time
OL,12,Flater.
OL,14,FSmith appeared via video link while
OL,15,FRycroft and the 17-year old boy
OL,16,Fattended in person. The defendants
OL,17,Fspoke only to confirm their names and
OL,18,Fdates of birth.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1777662668
OL,3,CTeenagers to face trial after denying
OL,4,Cgirl's murder
OL,6,FJudge Guy Kearl KC ordered the packed
OL,7,Fpublic galleries to be cleared during
OL,8,Fthe hearing after shouting disrupted
OL,9,Fthe proceedings.
OL,11,FThe judge eventually allowed one
OL,12,Ffamily member for each of the
OL,13,Fdefendants and the deceased to re-
OL,14,Fenter the courtroom.
OL,16,FAll three defendants were remanded
OL,17,Finto custody and a trial was
OL,18,Fprovisionally set for 10 November.
OL,20,FA 14-year old boy arrested last month
OL,21,Fon suspicion of murder remains on bail.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
