PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1777662668
OL,3,CTeenagers to face trial after denying
OL,4,Cgirl's murder
OL,6,FAn inquest opening in Wakefield heard
OL,7,FChloe, from Gomersal, suffered a fatal
OL,8,Fstab wound to the chest and was
OL,9,Fpronounced dead at Leeds General
OL,10,FInfirmary.
OL,12,FIn a tribute after her death, her
OL,13,Ffamily described Chloe as a
OL,14,F"beautiful, full of joy and a cheeky
OL,15,Fpersonality", adding that they were
OL,16,F"utterly devastated" by her loss.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
